  "texts": [
    "For training, we utilize all available sentences in both monolingual and parallel datasets.",
    "We apply regularization via word shuffling, dropping, and blanking during training.",
    "Optimization is achieved using Adam with a learning rate of 0.0001, and cross-entropy loss weights are adjusted throughout training.",
    "We conduct our training with a batch size of 16 and limit each epoch to 500,000 iterations.",
    "Additionally, we maintain a maximum sentence length restriction of 100 tokens during training."
